    "description": "Compu-Tron x3000 presents an alternate history and a narrative mystery to be uncovered.<br><br>In 1982, leading technology company C. Tech Industries released Compu-Tron x3000 (UK Edition) - a home computing assistant centred on education and utility applications.<br><br>Explore the features of this (at the time) ground-breaking application and see if you can uncover the mystery of what happened to C. Tech Industries. Where did they go? Why did they disappear? And who is D.A.V.E.?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Utilities: Calculation and Conversion Apps<br></li><li>Utilities: 5-Day UK Weather Forecast App<br></li><li>Education: UK History Timeline of Events<br></li><li>Education: Learn about The Solar System<br></li><li>Education: Learn about the Periodic Table of Elements<br></li><li>Games: A small selection of games to play with Compu-Tron<br></li><li>Mystery! Uncover the secrets behind C. Tech Industries and D.A.V.E.</li></ul>",
